videos.headline: Speight connects with Peoples-Jones for 37-yards
videos.description: Wilton Speight finds WR Donovan Peoples-Jones who turns up field for 37-yards, putting Michigan into Air Force territory.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Speight connects with Peoples-Jones for 37-yards) 2017/09/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Air Force's D clamps down to force Michigan fumble
videos.description: The Wolverines' offense continues to struggle in the first half as Air Force forces a fumble that Michigan recovers.  Jim Harbaugh's squad would go on to kick a field goal for a 9-6 lead at the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Air Force's D clamps down to force Michigan fumble) 2017/9/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Peoples-Jones returns punt for 79-yard Michigan TD
videos.description: Donovan Peoples-Jones scores the first Michigan touchdown of the day as he weaves his way 79-yards, giving the Wolverines a 16-6 lead over Air Force.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Peoples-Jones returns punt for 79-yard Michigan TD) 2017/09/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Air Force answers Michigan with rare 64-yard TD pass
videos.description: Arion Worthman finds WR Ronald Cleveland down the middle who turns up field for a 64-yard touchdown, cutting into the Michigan lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Air Force answers Michigan with rare 64-yard TD pass) 2017/09/16 ESHEET
